author: Chris Stuckmann
description:
From Osgood Perkins, the director of Longlegs & The Monkey, comes a new breed of nightmare. Don't miss the horror event of the season. KEEPER opens in theaters nationwide November 14th.

Chris Stuckmann reviews Frankenstein, starring Oscar Isaac, Jacob Elordi, Christoph Waltz, Mia Goth, Felix Kammerer, Charles Dance. Directed by Guillermo del Toro.
title: Frankenstein (2025) - Movie Review
